  <cite><strong>Andre in LA</strong> </cite> said 1 day later:<br />
  <p>I vote for moving the enhancements from Trac to the Wiki or another centralized repository. I want Rails to progress towards its core principles. Also, having the extra features as plugins will allow authors to make frequent enhancements and updates.</p>
